  <notes>
    Reference spec.md Section 7.4 for deployment strategy.
    
    Deployment commands:
    
    # BFF
    dotnet publish -c Release -o ./publish
    az webapp deploy --resource-group rg-spaarke-test \
        --name app-spe-bff-test \
        --src-path ./publish
    
    # Verify BFF
    curl https://app-spe-bff-test.azurewebsites.net/health
    
    # PCF
    cd power-platform/solutions
    pac solution import --path FileViewer_managed.zip \
        --environment https://spaarke-test.crm.dynamics.com
    
    Rollback procedure:
